{"tid":97562,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[mon開箱]eizo  ev2450","createTime":"2017-01-27T17:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-29T18:27:08.000Z","uid":60814,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec4034ae6185d51fa3e88e7628bfae8450af816","tid":97562,"uid":60814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:20:38.000Z","msg":"今日早到小小收工<br />\n走左去買隻mon等新年假個時爽皮下<br />\n<br />\n舊mon如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5upb4ier\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5upb4ier&h=3ce5809e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年是但買嘅benq gw2250 21.5&quot;<br />\n睇得耐就覺得麻麻<br />\n<br />\n行到中田都十五十六緊買幾大<br />\n因為我個位都要就埋隻臂同埋部notebook<br />\n<br />\n不過行過中田見到ezio係幾靚仔<br />\n同埋事前冇度尺，保守就買左24&quot;<br />\n2380 cash pay買入<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2c13qxn7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2c13qxn7&h=6aa89250&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開箱就大致如下<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zpy62a1x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzpy62a1x&h=cf1ed3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nmon, mon底座，power cord,  dvi,  hdmi同display port線各一<br />\n<br />\n個mon同個升降架一開始就上埋左一齊<br />\n但係我自已用臂，冇test過個升降架點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z2vi1w9o\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz2vi1w9o&h=1f37f576&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n折開埋升降架就咁，影多兩影啲input ports<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5svuodcf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5svuodcf&h=f9e82a9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vabgnpyr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvabgnpyr&h=91b02558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ju4hntwf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fju4hntwf&h=38ab4429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(mon右邊仲有個usb hub 1開2同埋audio port, 不過一開始冇為意亦都冇諗住用冇影到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n我地睇多次隻舊mon同埋後面咋線<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ou429etj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fou429etj&h=ae94c40a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/olzt6f0c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Folzt6f0c&h=2c2ace93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拆左隻舊mon落嚟一比對，發覺一樣大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隻舊mon粗邊框，新mon窄邊框好好j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yxs13kf8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyxs13kf8&h=cc0b15ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話咁快上左隻新mon上去<br />\n好在連啲線佈局都一鳩樣，唔係又要拉過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zmye0sd9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzmye0sd9&h=cc3de08b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家完成圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/80dnc3pu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F80dnc3pu&h=57d1dbac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個開箱換mon過程才不過十分鐘唔夠<br />\n都係搵支十字批拆同上螺絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好在隻mon size同inputs佈局同以前個隻一鳩樣<br />\n唔係又要上過隻臂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下先試下善用佢個usb hub先<br />\n<br />\n開箱完畢<br />\n打機過年"},{"pid":"5d7a38f108e51350988d854b758a52a3f63ba373","tid":97562,"uid":60814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:24:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47b6d492477745e86703ba53f2f468d3a97335b","tid":97562,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:41:24.000Z","msg":"eizo 真係好正<br />\n但佢d 高階mon 好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324df5a753ee59136eb84db307664dc1963cbe4c","tid":97562,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T01:30:59.000Z","msg":"Ev2450 根本垃圾<br />\n利申用緊"},{"pid":"985698c4d9753e472b801281435dc5f1f93d155b","tid":97562,"uid":71766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T02:40:30.000Z","msg":"8020?"},{"pid":"8183485859af72fa7d73d45a72e3033d390ec24a","tid":97562,"uid":35429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T03:36:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ev2450 根本垃圾<br />\n利申用緊</blockquote><br />\n點解垃圾？"},{"pid":"d7be44f5eb54f00714349f8617a9b6b21d2ef419","tid":97562,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:19:44.000Z","msg":"張枱亂到"},{"pid":"c764e28f52f8d5c3c2369160e1a3f9cb590413bc","tid":97562,"uid":36261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>張枱亂到</blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"9f2ec206e3b7d0a758b44178f3daaf95d095956f","tid":97562,"uid":49682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"eizo好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ef7d9ddcf074dcbd09e20931e499beec644c07","tid":97562,"uid":55593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:03:40.000Z","msg":"幾錢?"},{"pid":"ffe09793d087b4286fa0f4e006124201a0ad1bf0","tid":97562,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Eizo<br />\n正野！"},{"pid":"1911f1011981af617cc3192a97735fcf4293e377","tid":97562,"uid":60814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T08:32:11.